'''Vakkantham Suryanarayana Rao''' is an [[India]]n [[Telugu language]] author. He wrote several short stories and serialized novels for magazines and translated spiritual texts for the [[Tirumala Tirupati Devasthanams|Tirupati Tirumala Devasthanam]] and had friends among literary circles. His son [[Vakkantham Vamsi]] is a screenwriter in Telugu films.<ref>{{Cite news|title = Script by destiny|url = http://www.thehindu.com/todays-paper/tp-features/tp-metroplus/script-by-destiny/article4079360.ece|newspaper = The Hindu|date = 2012-11-09|access-date = 2015-08-06|issn = 0971-751X|language = en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title = Vakkantham Suryanarayana Rao Biography|url = http://www.pallibatani.com/view-8040-telugu-cinema-specials-vakkantham-suryanarayana-rao-biography.html|website = pallibatani|accessdate = 2015-08-18}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title = Vakkantham Suryanarayana Rao Profile|url = http://truetelugu.com/news.php?id=1242&title=Vakkantham-Suryanarayana-Rao-Profile-profile.html|accessdate = 2015-08-18}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title = Vakkantham Suryanarayana Rao Profile|url = http://www.cinejosh.com/news/5/42230/vakkantham-suryanarayana-rao-profile.html|accessdate = 2015-08-18}}</ref>


